data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home featuring first floor living on the countryside of Lancaster! This property offers a harmonious blend of rustic elegance and modern comfort. The neighborhood has  plenty to offer as you are drawn in by the beautiful landscaping and trees, almost captivating as the seasons are changing. Step inside to discover a seamlessly flowing floor plan. Walking through the front door you have an adequate living space. Next up is your full bath providing a private sanctuary for rest and rejuvenation. In addition, the bedrooms offer comfort and flexibility, ensuring plenty of space for family members or guests. Finished attic is also used as an extra bedroom. The property's allure extends outdoors. Step onto the expansive patio perfect for unwinding as you take in the view of your outdoor retreat. The vast grounds offer endless possibilities. Conveniently located in a sought-after area of Lancaster, this home provides easy access to the city's amenities while offering the tranquility of rural living. Don't miss this great opportunity to make 711 Bean Hill Road your new home!
